name: Tabacos Baez Serie SF - Toro
additionalNotes: Cuban-style sandwich tobaccos have never been blended more indulgently than in Tabacos Baez Serie SF. Patiently drafted in the world-famous My Father factory in Estelí, Nicaragua, under the watchful eye of legendary cigar-maker Jose ‘Pepin’ Garcia, Tabacos Baez SF is a glistening Nicaraguan puro.
